Isan’andininy
Tantaran’ny nitiavany ahy
(O! Tantara mamy)

(Nisoloan’i Jeso ‘zao ny heloko)

He ravo ny fanahy afaka ahiahy

(Fa voavonjinao eny ho mandrakizay)
